---

# 🌐 API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/clone` | Clone a public GitHub repository |
| POST | `/parser/parse` | Parse repository metadata |

More endpoints will be added as the project evolves.

