# 🚀 Getting Started

## Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/codepilot-ai.git
```

## Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Run the application

```bash
uvicorn main:app --reload
```

## Open Swagger UI

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
```

